{
  "uid": "graph2otel-m365-services",
  "title": "graph2otel: Microsoft 365 services overview",
  "description": "Exchange Online configuration and mail flow, SharePoint/OneDrive sharing and storage, Teams estate, and Microsoft 365 service health \u2014 plus the unified audit log twin. Generated by grafana/build_dashboard.py from spec/signal-catalog.json \u2014 edit grafana/boards/m365_services.py, not this JSON.",
